Planyo,is,a,flexible,online,booking,system,for,resources,such,as,hotels,holiday,apartments,yacht,rentals,driving,schools,tennis,courts,doctor,appointments,events,etc,The,Planyo,API,lets,users,perform,advanced,functions,and,automate,the,Planyo,reservation,system,e,g,import,resource,data,and,photos,into,your,site,make,automated,reservations,Planyo,is,available,in,languages,and,helps,users,manage,clients,bookings,by,handling,all,email,communication,with,the,clients,allowing,various,booking,confirmation,mechanisms,handling,payments,also,online,credit,card,payments,with,PayPal,or,Moneybookers,printing,invoices,etc,The,API,uses,RESTful,protocol,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON